languages.text: "Потому что я не культистка смерти с промытыми мозгами. Потому что хочу жить. Потому что есть люди, которым я обязана".

traits.locale_text: "Потому что я не культистка смерти с промытыми мозгами. Потому что хочу жить. Потому что есть люди, которым я обязана".

languages.text: "Because I'm not a brainwashed death cultist. Because I want to live. Because there are people counting on me. I owe it to them to stick around."

languages.text: «Porque no soy una fanática de la muerte. Porque quiero vivir. Porque hay gente que cuenta conmigo. Les debo a todos ellos el seguir aquí».
languages.original_text: "Because I'm not a brainwashed death cultist. Because I want to live. Because there are people counting on me. I owe it to them to stick around."

languages.text: 「だって、あたいは死のカルトに洗脳されてないし。生きていたいし。あたしを頼りにしてる人たちがいるし。恩があるから、まだ死ぬわけにはいかないの」
languages.original_text: "Because I'm not a brainwashed death cultist. Because I want to live. Because there are people counting on me. I owe it to them to stick around."

languages.text: “因为我可不是被洗了脑的拜死教教徒。因为我想活下去，因为还有人指望我呢。就算是为了他们，我也得活下去。”
languages.original_text: "Because I'm not a brainwashed death cultist. Because I want to live. Because there are people counting on me. I owe it to them to stick around."

languages.text: "Weil ich keine Todeskultistin bin. Weil ich leben will. Weil sich Leute auf mich verlassen. Ich bin es ihnen schuldig, zu bleiben."
languages.original_text: "Because I'm not a brainwashed death cultist. Because I want to live. Because there are people counting on me. I owe it to them to stick around."

languages.text: « Parce que je ne suis pas un abruti de cultiste de la mort. Parce que je veux vivre. Parce qu'il est des gens qui comptent sur moi. Je leur dois de m'accrocher. »
languages.original_text: "Because I'm not a brainwashed death cultist. Because I want to live. Because there are people counting on me. I owe it to them to stick around."
"Because I'm not a brainwashed death cultist. Because I want to live. Because there are people counting on me. I owe it to them to stick around."

languages.text: "Çünkü beyni yıkanmış ölüm tarikatçısının teki değilim. Çünkü yaşamak istiyorum. Çünkü bana güvenen insanlar var. Onlara yaşamaya devam etmeyi borçluyum."
languages.original_text: "Because I'm not a brainwashed death cultist. Because I want to live. Because there are people counting on me. I owe it to them to stick around."
